## Entity Relationship Summary

```
workflows (1)
  ŌööŌöĆŌöĆ workflow_steps (many)          ON DELETE CASCADE
  ŌööŌöĆŌöĆ workflow_executions (many)     ON DELETE RESTRICT

workflow_executions (1)
  ŌööŌöĆŌöĆ workflow_execution_steps (many) ON DELETE CASCADE

scheduled_jobs (1)
  ŌööŌöĆŌöĆ job_results (many)             no FK constraint (soft ref)
  ŌööŌöĆŌöĆ workflow_executions            no FK constraint (workflow_resume jobs only)
```

