## Indexes Worth Knowing

| Table | Index | Used for |
|-------|-------|----------|
| `workflow_steps` | `uk_workflow_step (workflow_id, step_number)` | Uniqueness + fast step lookup by workflow |
| `workflow_executions` | `idx_workflow_status (workflow_id, status)` | Filtering executions by workflow + status |
| `workflow_executions` | `idx_status (status)` | Recovery queries, list by status |
| `workflow_execution_steps` | `idx_execution_step (execution_id, step_number, executed_at DESC)` | Step history retrieval |
| `scheduled_jobs` | `idx_scheduled_pending (status, scheduled_time)` | The core claim query in process-jobs |